 like a computer. I don't know. I mean, you know. So, we have all these numbers, and we can add them and subtract them and add them. TIMES them even. Did you know that? We can times them OR divide them, they don't tell you that, and I'll tell you, no one is better at the order of operations than me. You wouldn't believe it. So, we're gonna be the best on 2+2, believe me.&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50f940630d3efcc80574c58240d88525dfbbb82","tid":340706,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到演說點可以唔提 元首？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHilter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eA6wmocKPtw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeA6wmocKPtw&d=AT6lbvV0ajZKnYXeFQ9HR6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=175038ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eA6wmocKPtw</a></blockquote><br />\n佢選總統個陣全國巡迴拉票  每日五場演說 仲要每場演說都扣人心弦 真係冇人癲得過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf8bc0741d4979466883c4cc6f0213738c5f653","tid":340706,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"以前J開奥巴馬"},{"pid":"d0f90848b0c97b4a44965e44e70d1118d0372e0c","tid":340706,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主有冇speeches that changed the world 呢本書</blockquote><br />\n冇呀 如果有既我都想睇下</blockquote><br />\n入面有哂各國改變歷史時刻的演說 可以留意下"},{"pid":"f1dc61e7749650292cbd46246e1cabcbdc65069e","tid":340706,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited